 from other groups are also summarized, and we argue\nthat further, independent studies are needed to verify their predictions.\nCombined with our previous work, the results presented here provide refined\nestimates of HZs around main-sequence stars and provide a step towards a more\ncomprehensive analysis of HZs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Apr 2014 19:57:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 May 2014 13:44:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
