y efficient BH sources,\nwhile the former plane proposed by Merloni et al. and Falcke et al. may be most\nsuitable for radiatively inefficient sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Apr 2014 20:02:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
