m, we find that synchrotron emission can account for at most\n20% of the reported BICEP2 signal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Apr 2014 20:28:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Aug 2014 09:55:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-04"}
