 regular and\nchaotic orbits and to quantify their chaoticity. We find that even a small\nmisalignment induces chaotic motion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Apr 2014 13:46:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 May 2014 12:26:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-28"}
